The evidence with the title 'A $15 minimum wage would cost 6.6 million jobs. Yes, 6,600,000 ... ' says Aug 7, 2015  ... We are in the middle of one of those delightful mass delusions to which  ... To try to make $ 15 an hour the national minimum wage for the US . 6.6 million, yes, that's 6,600,000 jobs will be lost .  ... Earning between $ 7.25 and $10.10 getting a raise,  ... Raising the minimum wage will create jobs , not kill them! 
